<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c3">{بِسْمِ اللَّهِ الرَّحْمَنِ الرَّحِيمِ}</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>١ - {الْقَارِعَةُ <span class="c2">(١)</span> مَا الْقَارِعَةُ <span class="c2">(٢)</span> وَمَا أَدْرَاكَ مَا الْقَارِعَةُ <span class="c2">(٣)</span> يَوْمَ يَكُونُ النَّاسُ كَالْفَرَاشِ} <span class="c2">(١)</span> وهي <span class="c2">(٢)</span> الطير التي <span class="c2">(٣)</span> تتساقط في النَّار <span class="c2">(٤)</span>.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c3">{الْمَبْثُوثِ}</span> المتفرق <span class="c2">(٥)</span>.<span class="c5"> قال الفراء:</span> كغوغاء الجراد يركب بعضه بعضًا من الهول <span class="c2">(٦)</span>.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>٥ - {وَتَكُونُ الْجِبَالُ كَالْعِهْنِ الْمَنْفُوشِ <span class="c2">(٥)</span>}<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>كالصوف المصبوغ المندوف <span class="c2">(٧)</span>.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>٦ - {فَأَمَّا مَنْ ثَقُلَتْ مَوَازِينُهُ <span class="c2">(٦)</span> فَهُوَ فِي عِيشَةٍ رَاضِيَةٍ}<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c2">(مرضية في الجنة)</span> <span class="c2">(٨)</span> <span class="c2">(٩)</span>.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>٨ - {وَأَمَّا مَنْ خَفَّتْ مَوَازِينُهُ <span class="c2">(٨)</span> فَأُمُّهُ هَاوِيَةٌ <span class="c2">(٩)</span>}<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
